						<summary>

						<p>Stone lying in the field called Muddappana-bīḷu.</p>						

						<p>Achyutarāya, 1536 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This fragmentary record refers to the reign of Achyutarāya, all other details being lost. It is dated the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Durmukhi, Śrāvaṇa śu. 6,</hi> the details being insufficient for verification. The <hi rend="italic">tithi</hi> corresponds to <hi rend="bold">1536 A.D., October 20,</hi> the cyclic year falling in the reign-period of Achyutarāya.</p>						

						</summary>
